Description: Will an ally of Naruto sacrifice his own life to prevent Naruto from risking his own?
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 57
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: The story of "Alice’s Adventures in Wonderland" is retold, manga-style.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF HEARTS, VOL. 1
Author: Quinrose and Soumei Hoshino

Description: In this reimagining of Lewis Carroll's "Alice's Adventures in Wonderland," the Cheshire Cat, disguised as a human named Boris, vies for Alice's affections.
Title: ALICE IN THE COUNTRY OF CLOVER: CHESHIRE CAT WALTZ, VOL. 1
Author: QuinRose and Mamenosuke Fujimaru

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 10
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: A mysterious disease has turned a high school’s student body into zombies.
Title: HIGHSCHOOL OF THE DEAD, VOL. 7
Author: Daisuke Sato

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 14
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Welcome to the Death Weapon Meister Academy, where students learn how to control their armaments in classes like NOT (Normally Overcome Targets) and EAT (Especially Advantaged Talent).
Title: SOUL EATER NOT!, VOL. 1
Author: Atsushi Ohkubo

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 6
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 43
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Journey to Ikebukuro, a Japanese city with lots of unusual activity, including the Black Biker, who is rumored to be headless.
Title: DURARARA!!, VOL. 3
Author: Ryohgo Narita
